# Songs_website
Features (APIs):
Users:
    End-user
    Admin
Use cases:
    JWT Authentication
    Admin can
        Schedule a process to add a song by specifying a future time
End-user can
      Login/Signup/Forgot Password
      View all available songs
      Search/Filter songs based on name search and tags
      Like a song
      Add song to favorite
      Create an album (private/public albums)
      List albums
      Add songs to the particular album
      Add comments on songs
      Follow a particular album, gets a notification when a new song is added
      Deployment (Heroku/AWS)
